Layers are a common concept in
image manipulation software.

2
00:00:03,530 --> 00:00:07,143
For instance, at Udacity we use a piece
of software called SketchBook Pro to

3
00:00:07,143 --> 00:00:09,790
make drawings like
the ones you see here.

4
00:00:09,790 --> 00:00:12,700
And we use layers to make
it easy to separate and

5
00:00:12,700 --> 00:00:14,450
edit different parts of our drawings.

6
00:00:14,450 --> 00:00:15,560
Here let me show you.

7
00:00:15,560 --> 00:00:18,390
These are the menu options I
get when I'm using SketchBook.

8
00:00:18,390 --> 00:00:20,780
And this one here gives me
control over the layers.

9
00:00:20,780 --> 00:00:22,990
For instance, I can hide the background.

10
00:00:22,990 --> 00:00:25,800
I can hide the sidebar for the stories.

11
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:30,300
In fact, I will select this story, and
I can move it around the page without

12
00:00:30,300 --> 00:00:33,320
